Class ApplicantMain

Object
ApplicantMain
All Implemented Interfaces:
IUserMain<Applicant>
public class ApplicantMain extends Object implements IUserMain<Applicant>
The ApplicantMain class provides the main interface for applicants to interact with the BTO system. It allows applicants to view projects, apply for projects, manage enquiries, and book flats.
